  \ref{defn-runtime-pointer-size} indicating the message that is to be
  verified.
  
  \item \tmverbatim{key}: a 32-bit pointer to the buffer containing the
  256-bit public key.
  
  \item \tmverbatim{return}: a i32 integer value equal to \tmverbatim{1} if
